snippet.title: Gameplay Trailer Bird Feather Aquamarine World - Wishlist on Steam!
snippet.description:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2874360/Bird_Feather_Aquamarine_World/ - Steam Bird Feather Aquamarine World. Add game to wishlist on Steam! This game created by solo indie game developer from Ukraine. https://discord.com/invite/MkghCsHxxR - Andrium Games. You are bird. Just fly! Collect feathers in open world bird game. Collect more feathers to unlock nice Kingfisher photos. After collect all feathers you can just fly and enjoy! Kingfisher bird realistic animation. Pretty low-poly art style and graphics. 12 photos to unlock. Three worlds. Bonus Unlimited game mode. Game powered by Unreal Engine 5.

System requirements: 390 MB free drive space. GPU DirextX 12 support. The game is available for Windows. A 64-bit processor and a 64-bit operating system are required to run the game.

Flight, Collectathon, Birds, 3D, Nature, Open World, Indie, Relaxing, Nonlinear, Exploration, Adventure, Third Person, Singleplayer, Simulation, Family Friendly, Colorful, Cute, Minimalist, new game, new steam games.

Special thanks to PULSAR BYTES.
